descript.purpose: Identifies township and incorporated area boundaries.
descript.supplinf: It is believed the shapefiles for this feature were downloaded from indinidual counties prior to July, 2007. In July 2007, OKI staff began updating this feature. County, township and municipal entities within the OKI coverage area were contacted for updates. These entities provided OKI with digital, hard copy, or no updates. Hard copy information was digitized by OKI staff. The boundaries were then aligned to coincide (align) with each other. This was accomplished by using "heirarchy" to realign boundaries, that is, towship boundaries were aligned with county boundaries, municipalites were aligned with county or township boundaries, and municipal boundaries were aligned with adjacent municipalities.
